column1: 1️⃣ Basic Level (Shuruat ke liye enough)

Python basics: variables
column6: while)

column1: Libraries ka basic use:
pandas → data load
numpy → basic maths
CSV/Excel read & write (pd.read_csv
📌 Time to learn: 2–4 weeks (part-time practice)
2️⃣ Intermediate Level (Professional kaam ke liye)
Is stage pe tum data ko deep clean & transform kar sakte ho.
Date/time data handling (pd.to_datetime
scikit-learn basics → data split
📌 Time to learn: 2–3 months (with projects)
3️⃣ Advanced Level (Analytics + Machine Learning)
Yeh tab zaroori hota hai jab tum ML/AI touch karna chahte ho.
📌 Time to learn: 6+ months (depending on depth)
💡 Shortcut Tip: Agar tumhara focus sirf data analysis & visualization hai

column1: Main tumhari situation ke hisaab se direct roadmap de raha hoon — no time waste mode me.
1️⃣ Tumhari Current Skills ka Analysis
C++ ka experience: matlab tumko programming logic already aata hai ✅
20 din full 3 ghante daily
Baad me 2 ghante daily
Goal: Portfolio banake earning start karni in 2 months 🚀
2️⃣ Kya Karna Chahiye (Step-by-Step)
Phase 1 — Direct Data Tools Jump (Next 20 days)
Forget file handling for now. Tumhare liye ab pandas + matplotlib + seaborn hi main weapons hain.
Why? Freelance & jobs me koi tumse “file read ka syntax” nahi puchega — woh bolega “yeh sales data visualize karo.”
Day 1–3: Pandas basics — read CSV/Excel
column6: boolean indexing.

column1: Day 15–20: Mini projects (Kaggle datasets) — Sales Analysis
💡 Tip: Kaggle ke datasets uthao
column2: Google pe “pandas [problem]” search karke solve karo.

column1: Phase 2 — Portfolio Building (Next 40 days)
Day 21–30: 3 complete projects bana ke GitHub pe push karo:
Sales Dashboard (Excel + Pandas + Seaborn)
Netflix Dataset Analysis
Weather Data Visualization
Day 31–40: Power BI seekho (free YouTube course) — iska advantage: clients ko professional dashboard chahiye hota hai.
Day 41–50: Excel advanced functions (VLOOKUP
Day 51–60: Fiverr/Upwork pe profile banao
3️⃣ Tumhare Sawalon ka Seedha Jawaab
Q1: “File handling seekhun ya direct Pandas?”
➡ Direct Pandas. File handling baad me
Q2: “Itni Python ke baad Pandas samajh aa jayega?”
➡ Bilkul. Tumhari C++ background + basic Python is enough. Thoda syntax difference hoga
Q3: “Excel & Power BI kab seekhun?”

column2: portfolio phase me (Day 31 se). Kyunki ye tumhe freelance market me instantly sellable skill dega.

column1: Q4: “Aage AI specialization lena theek rahega?”
➡ Bohot theek. Data analysis + visualization is the foundation of AI/ML. Tum ab jo seekhoge
column2: wahi tumhe AI me aage edge dega.

column1: 4️⃣ Money in 2 Months — Realistic Expectation
Month 1 end: Tum portfolio ready kar loge (3–4 projects GitHub pe).
Month 2 mid: Fiverr/Upwork pe data cleaning
